value: Breeds in Greenland, Iceland, northern British Isles (formerly) northern Europe and Asia east to Anadyr and Kamchatka south to the eastern Mediterranean (formerly to Egypt and the Red Sea), Mesopotamia, Persia and Japan. Casually or in winter to northern Africa, northwestern India, southern China and the Aleutian Islands.
